Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time to transition from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time it takes to resolve a case after 'Accepted + Wait' is performed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Accepted + Wait' followed by 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Completed + Closed' in cases passing through 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Assigned' across different countries
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Wait' in cases that also include 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Resolved' in the context of VINST system
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time it takes 'Accepted + Wait' after the execution of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Average time for 'Accepted + Wait' grouped by 'organization country'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases ending with 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time it takes the 'Accepted + Wait' to be done before reaching 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time for 'Accepted + Wait' in cases with 'Completed + In Call' to understand its impact on the process flow.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
